reviews.snippet:
Not recommended... You need to wait hours to get in AND to get your meals. A lot of clients gave up before us. We were 3 and it took 2 hours to receive a burger with exactly 8 French fries cause they forgot our orders. It's also totally overpriced for the quality that they serve unfortunately.

Can't understand how they have +5 stars
